<p>An Indian Air Force HAL Tejas light combat aircraft crashed during a flying display at the Dubai Airshow on Friday at Al Maktoum International Airport, killing the pilot, according to the IAF and Dubai Government Media Office [apnews.com#1][al-monitor.com#1]. Emergency crews responded as black smoke rose from the site, and the IAF said it has ordered a court of inquiry to determine the cause [scmp.com#1][ndtv.com#1][al-monitor.com#2][dawn.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/1q_lIvGp3ZnPCg9-lDDP-yZHXW20cBlhX0nneU3wvO82-KxHX_IqxHdozAQgbu861WuKC0sA0Pavhlew4sy2IVCQ0UhEwqtjrSt2kLeaW-m4' alt='Screengrab showing smoke after an Indian jet crashed at the Dubai Airshow on November 21, 2025.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Crash timing: The aircraft went down around 2:10pm local time near the Dubai Airshow area at Al Maktoum International Airport [dawn.com#1][rt.com#1]</li><li>Emergency response: Police vehicles, ambulances and a helicopter rushed to the site and used firefighting foam to extinguish the blaze [scmp.com#1]</li><li>Pilot outcome: The pilot sustained fatal injuries; reports said the pilot was unable to eject [al-monitor.com#1][apnews.com#1]</li><li>Investigation: The Indian Air Force announced a court of inquiry, and India’s embassy said it is in touch with UAE authorities [al-monitor.com#2][dawn.com#1]</li><li>Program context: The Tejas is India’s indigenous light combat aircraft; this is the second recorded Tejas crash, and India recently ordered 97 upgraded Mk1A jets worth about $7 billion [aljazeera.com#2][dawn.com#1]</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Indian Air Force: The IAF confirmed the pilot’s death and said a court of inquiry will ascertain the cause [dawn.com#1][al-monitor.com#2] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn, Al-Monitor</a>)</li><li>Dubai Government Media Office: Confirmed the “tragic death of the pilot” following the crash at the airshow [al-monitor.com#1] (<a href='https://www.al-monitor.com/originals/2025/11/indian-warplane-crashes-dubai-airshow-killing-pilot'>Al-Monitor</a>)</li><li>Indian Embassy in UAE: Said it is in contact with UAE authorities after the incident [dawn.com#1] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/tejas-fighter-jet-crashes-at-dubai-air-show-9676350#publisher=newsstand'>Pilot Dies As Tejas Fighter Jet Crashes, Bursts Into Flames At Dubai Air Show</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/south-asia/article/3333738/indian-air-force-pilot-dies-tejas-jet-crash-during-dubai-air-show-demonstration'>Indian Air Force pilot dies in Tejas crash during Dubai Air Show demonstration</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.al-monitor.com/originals/2025/11/indian-warplane-crashes-dubai-airshow-killing-pilot'>Indian warplane crashes at Dubai Airshow, killing pilot</a> - al-monitor.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/11/21/pilot-killed-as-fighter-jet-crashes-at-dubai-airshow'>Pilot killed as fighter jet crashes at Dubai Airshow</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/video/2025/11/21/indian-combat-jet-crashes-at-dubai-airshow-killing-pilot'>Indian combat jet crashes at Dubai Airshow, killing pilot</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rt.com/india/628102-ias-pilot-dead-dubai-crash/'>Pilot killed as Indian fighter jet crashes at Dubai Airshow (VIDEO)</a> - rt.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/indian-air-force-tejas-jet-crashes-at-dubai-air-show/a-74835184'>Indian Air Force Tejas jet crashes at Dubai Air Show</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>India’s indigenous Tejas fighter aircraft crashes at Dubai Air Show</a> - dawn.com</li><li><a href='https://www.